$ govctl adr new Compat Test
Created ADR: gov/adr/ADR-XXXX-compat-test.toml
exit: 0

$ govctl adr set ADR-0001 content.decision A dotted decision
Set ADR-0001.decision = A dotted decision
exit: 0

$ govctl adr get ADR-0001 content.decision
A dotted decision
exit: 0

$ govctl adr set ADR-0001 govctl.title Compat Title
Set ADR-0001.title = Compat Title
exit: 0

$ govctl adr get ADR-0001 govctl.title
Compat Title
exit: 0
